summary: model of the ocarina of time, similar to the one seen in ocarina of time
descriptionHtml:
the ocarina model that i created, originally for matt13382 and his zelda mod. this is published as a resource. keep in mind that this is one of my first completed models, and i strongly encourage users to modify or enhance the model, however any modifications intended for sharing MUST be reuploaded to my page for users to download. credit will be given.

enjoy!

model details:
model is unscaled and untextured, 7,006 triangles, saved as a .obj
author: greg079
